snippet.title: Dune | Official Main Trailer
snippet.description:
IT’S TIME. #DuneMovie coming October 22.

-----------------
https://www.instagram.com/dunemovie/
https://www.facebook.com/dune
https://twitter.com/dunemovie 
-----------------

Oscar nominee Denis Villeneuve (“Arrival,” “Blade Runner 2049”) directs Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures’ “Dune,” the big-screen adaptation of Frank Herbert’s seminal bestseller of the same name.

A mythic and emotionally charged hero’s journey, “Dune” tells the story of Paul Atreides, a brilliant and gifted young man born into a great destiny beyond his understanding, who must travel to the most dangerous planet in the universe to ensure the future of his family and his people. As malevolent forces explode into conflict over the planet’s exclusive supply of the most precious resource in existence—a commodity capable of unlocking humanity’s greatest potential—only those who can conquer their fear will survive.

The film stars Oscar nominee Timothée Chalamet (“Call Me by Your Name,” “Little Women”), Rebecca Ferguson (“Stephen King’s Doctor Sleep,” “Mission: Impossible – Fallout”), Oscar Isaac (the “Star Wars” franchise) Oscar nominee Josh Brolin (“Milk,” “Avengers: Infinity War”), Stellan Skarsgård (HBO’s “Chernobyl,” “Avengers: Age of Ultron”), Dave Bautista (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “Avengers: Endgame”), Stephen McKinley Henderson (“Fences,” “Lady Bird”), Zendaya (“Spider-Man: Homecoming,” HBO’s “Euphoria”), Chang Chen (“Mr. Long,” “Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon”), David Dastmalchian (“Blade Runner 2049,” “The Dark Knight”), Sharon Duncan-Brewster (“Rogue One: A Star Wars Story,” Netflix’s “Sex Education”), with Oscar nominee Charlotte Rampling (“45 Years,” “Assassin’s Creed”), with Jason Momoa (“Aquaman,” HBO’s “Game of Thrones”), and Oscar winner Javier Bardem (“No Country for Old Men,” “Skyfall”).

Villeneuve directed “Dune” from a screenplay by Jon Spaihts and Villeneuve and Eric Roth based on the novel of the same name written by Frank Herbert. Villeneuve also produced the film with Mary Parent, Cale Boyter and Joe Caracciolo, Jr. The executive producers are Tanya Lapointe, Joshua Grode, Herbert W. Gains, Jon Spaihts, Thomas Tull, Brian Herbert, Byron Merritt and Kim Herbert.

Behind the scenes, Villeneuve reteamed with two-time Oscar-nominated production designer Patrice Vermette (“Arrival,” “Sicario,” “The Young Victoria”), two-time Oscar-nominated editor Joe Walker (“Blade Runner 2049,” “Arrival,” “12 Years a Slave”), two-time Oscar-winning visual effects supervisor Paul Lambert (“First Man,” “Blade Runner 2049”), and Oscar-winning special effects supervisor Gerd Nefzer (“Blade Runner 2049”). He also collaborated for the first time with Oscar-nominated director of photography Greig Fraser (“Lion,” “Zero Dark Thirty,” “Rogue One: A Star Wars Story”); three-time Oscar-nominated costume designer Jacqueline West (“The Revenant,” “The Curious Case of Benjamin Button,” “Quills”) and costume designer Robert Morgan; and stunt coordinator Tom Struthers (“The Dark Knight” trilogy, “Inception”). Oscar-winning and multiple Oscar-nominated composer Hans Zimmer (“Blade Runner 2049,” “Inception,” “Gladiator,” “The Lion King”) is creating the score.

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present a Legendary Pictures Production, a Film by Denis Villeneuve, “Dune.” The film is slated to be released in select theaters in 2D and 3D and IMAX and on HBO Max on October 22, 2021 and will be available on HBO Max’s Ad-Free plan in 4K UHD, HDR10, Dolby Vision and Dolby Atmos (English Only) on supported devices for 31 days from theatrical release.

The film has been rated PG-13 for sequences of strong violence, some disturbing images and suggestive material.

snippet.title: Battlefield 2042 | Battlefield Portal Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Battlefield™ 2042 starting October 22, 2021

Discover Battlefield Portal – an all-new, community-driven platform where players will be able to change the rules of war by creating, sharing and discovering unexpected battles from Battlefield’s iconic past, present, and future.

Battlefield 2042 is a first-person shooter that marks the return to the iconic all-out warfare of the franchise. Adapt and overcome in a near-future world transformed by disorder. Squad up and bring a cutting-edge arsenal into dynamically-changing battlegrounds supporting 128 players*, unprecedented scale, and epic destruction.

Pre-order now for early Open Beta access and more: http://x.ea.com/68944 

Find out more about Battlefield: http://x.ea.com/68674

See the Battlefield 2042 Official Reveal Trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E

See the Battlefield 2042 Official Gameplay Trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss 

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/battlefield
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/battlefield
Follow us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/battlefield

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal
*Supported on Xbox Series X|S, PC and PlayStation®5. Xbox One and PlayStation®4 will be locked at 64 players

localizations.ja.title: Battlefield 2042 | 「バトルフィールド・ポータル」公式トレーラー
localizations.ja.description:
2021年10月22日に開幕する「Battlefield™ 2042」に参戦せよ

「バトルフィールド・ポータル」 – プレイヤーが「Battlefield」の象徴的な過去、現代、未来の戦場から、独自のルールで進行する予測不可能なバトルを創り出し、共有し、発見できる、全く新しいコミュニティー主導のプラットフォーム「バトルフィールド・ポータル」について紹介！

「Battlefield 2042」はシリーズの象徴である全面戦争への回帰を示す、ファーストパーソン・シューティングゲーム。無秩序によって変化した近未来の世界に適応し、戦いを乗り越えよ。128人のプレイヤーに対応（※）。分隊を編成し、最先端の武装を携え、空前のスケールと壮大な破壊によってもたらされる、激動の戦場に舞い降りるのだ。

今すぐ予約して、オープンベータへのアーリーアクセス権などの特典を獲得しよう: http://x.ea.com/68944

「Battlefield」の詳細を確認: http://x.ea.com/68674

「Battlefield 2042」公式発表トレーラーを視聴: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E

「Battlefield 2042」公式ゲームプレイ・トレーラーを視聴: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss

Twitterでフォロー: https://twitter.com/battlefield
Instagramでフォロー: https://www.instagram.com/battlefield
Facebookでフォロー: https://www.facebook.com/battlefield

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal
※Xbox Series X|S、PC、およびPlayStation®5にのみ対応。Xbox OneおよびPlayStation®4ではプレイヤー数が64人に限定されます。
localizations.zh.title: 《战地风云 2042》|《战地风云》门户官方预告片
localizations.zh.description:
从 2021 年 10 月 22 日起游玩《战地风云 2042》

探索《战地风云》门户——这是一个以社区为主导的全新平台，玩家可以在这里创建、分享和探索《战地风云》中标志性的过去、现在和未来中出人意料的战斗，以此改变战争的规则！

《战地风云 2042》是一款第一人称射击游戏，本作将带领玩家重返该系列标志性的全面战争。适应并征服一个因失序而面目全非的近未来世界组成小队，带上尖端武器，前往变化无常的战场，最多支持 128 名玩家*，规模史无前例，让您体验史诗般的毁灭。

立即预购即可抢先体验 Beta 公测以及更多内容：http://x.ea.com/68944

深入了解《战地风云》：http://x.ea.com/68674

观看《战地风云 2042》官方揭露预告片：https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E

观看《战地风云 2042》官方游戏预告片：https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss

在 Twitter 上关注我们：https://twitter.com/battlefield
在 Instagram 上关注我们：https://www.instagram.com/battlefield
在 Facebook 上关注我们：https://www.facebook.com/battlefield

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal
*支持 Xbox Series X|S、PC 和 PlayStation®5。Xbox One 和 PlayStation®4 将限定为 64 名玩家
localizations.ar.title: Battlefield 2042 | إعلان Battlefield Portal الرسمي
localizations.ar.description:
استمتع بلعب Battlefield™ 2042 بداية من 22 أكتوبر 2021

اكتشف Battlefield Portal – منصة جديدة كليًا مُدارة بواسطة المجتمع، حيث يمكن للاعبين تغيير قواعد الحرب عن طريق إنشاء معارك غير متوقعة ومشاركتها واكتشافها من الأحداث السابقة والحالية والمستقبلية المميّزة من Battlefield.

Battlefield 2042 هي لعبة تصويب من منظور الشخص الأول تمثل العودة إلى الحرب الشاملة الأيقونية للسلسلة. تكيَّف مع الظروف وتغلب عليها في عالم تدور أحداثه في المستقبل القريب تحول بفعل الاضطرابات والفوضى. شكّل فرقة وأحضر ترسانة متطورة إلى ساحات المعارك المتغيرة بشكل ديناميكي التي تدعم 128 لاعبًا*، ونطاقًا غير مسبوق، وتدميرًا ملحميًا.

اطلب مسبقًا الآن للحصول على وصول مبكّر إلى إصدار بيتا المفتوح، وغير ذلك الكثير: http://x.ea.com/68944 

اعرف المزيد عن Battlefield‏: http://x.ea.com/68674 

شاهد الإعلان الرسمي للكشف عن Battlefield 2042: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E 

شاهد الإعلان الرسمي لأسلوب اللعب في Battlefield 2042: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss 

تابعنا على تويتر: https://twitter.com/battlefield 
تابعنا على إنستجرام: https://www.instagram.com/battlefield 
تابعنا على فيسبوك: https://www.facebook.com/battlefield 

‎#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal

localizations.it.title: Battlefield 2042 | Trailer ufficiale Battlefield Portal
localizations.it.description:
Gioca a Battlefield™ 2042 dal 22 ottobre 2021

Scopri Battlefield Portal, una nuova piattaforma basata sulla community, con cui i giocatori possono cambiare le regole della guerra creando, condividendo e scoprendo battaglie inattese nel passato, nel presente e nel futuro di Battlefield!

Battlefield 2042 è uno sparatutto in prima persona che segna il ritorno dell'iconica guerra totale della serie. Adattati per vincere in un mondo trasformato dal caos nel prossimo futuro. Forma una squadra e porta un arsenale all'avanguardia in campi di battaglia in costante mutamento con supporto per 128 giocatori*, scala senza precedenti e distruzione epica.

Prenota subito per ottenere l'accesso anticipato all'Open Beta e altro ancora: http://x.ea.com/68944 

Scopri di più su Battlefield: http://x.ea.com/68674 

Guarda il trailer di presentazione ufficiale di Battlefield 2042: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E 

Battlefield 2042 - Trailer di gioco ufficiale: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss 

Seguici su Twitter: https://twitter.com/battlefield 
Seguici su Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/battlefield 
Seguici su Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/battlefield 

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal
*Supportati su Xbox Series X|S, PC e PlayStation®5. Xbox One e PlayStation®4 supporteranno 64 giocatori.
localizations.pt-BR.title: Battlefield 2042 | Trailer oficial de Battlefield Portal
localizations.pt-BR.description:
Jogue Battlefield™ 2042 a partir de 22 de outubro de 2021

Descubra o Battlefield Portal - uma plataforma inédita voltada para a comunidade, em que quem joga poderá mudar as regras da guerra criando, compartilhando e descobrindo batalhas inesperadas do passado, presente e futuro icônicos de Battlefield.

Battlefield 2042 é um jogo de tiro em primeira pessoa que marca o retorno à emblemática guerra total da franquia. Mostre que você é capaz de se adaptar e superar um mundo num futuro próximo, transformado pela desordem. Forme um pelotão e leve um arsenal de ponta para campos de batalha dinâmicos com capacidade para 128 pessoas*, escala sem precedentes e destruição épica.

Reserve agora para ter acesso antecipado ao Beta Aberto e mais: http://x.ea.com/68944

Saiba mais sobre Battlefield: http://x.ea.com/68674

Assista ao trailer de anúncio oficial de Battlefield 2042: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E

Assista ao trailer de jogabilidade oficial de Battlefield 2042: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss

Siga-nos no Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/battlefield

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal

localizations.de.title: Battlefield 2042 | Battlefield Portal – Offizieller Trailer
localizations.de.description:
Spiele Battlefield™ 2042 ab dem 22. Oktober 2021

Entdecke Battlefield Portal – eine brandneue Community-Plattform, auf der du die Regeln des Krieges ändern kannst, indem du unerwartete Schlachten aus der Vergangenheit, Gegenwart und Zukunft von Battlefield erstellen, teilen und entdecken kannst.

Battlefield 2042 ist ein First-Person-Shooter, der einmal mehr das ganze Ausmaß des Krieges präsentiert. Passe dich an eine aus den Fugen geratene Welt in naher Zukunft an und überlebe. Bilde einen Trupp und kämpfe mit einem topmodernen Arsenal auf dynamischen Schlachtfeldern für 128 Spieler* in einer nie da gewesenen Größenordnung mit epischer Zerstörung.

Jetzt vorbestellen, um Early Access zur offenen Beta und mehr zu erhalten: http://x.ea.com/68944 

Mehr über Battlefield erfahren: http://x.ea.com/68674 

Offiziellen Battlefield 2042 Reveal-Trailer ansehen: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E 

Offiziellen Battlefield 2042 Gameplay-Trailer ansehen: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss 

Folge uns auf Twitter: https://twitter.com/battlefield 
Folge uns auf Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/battlefield 
Folge uns auf Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/battlefield 

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal
*Auf Xbox Series X|S, PC und PlayStation®5 unterstützt. Xbox One und PlayStation®4 unterstützen maximal 64 Spieler.
localizations.zh-TW.title: 《戰地風雲 2042》|《戰地風雲》入口官方預告片
localizations.zh-TW.description:
從 2021 年 10 月 22 日起遊玩《戰地風雲 2042》

探索《戰地風雲》入口——在這個以社群為本的全新平台中，玩家可以一同創造、分享和探索，並且透過《戰地風雲》精彩的過去、現在與未來踏入出乎意料的戰場，改變戰爭規則。

localizations.fr.title: Battlefield 2042 | Trailer officiel de Battlefield Portal
localizations.fr.description:
Jouez à Battlefield™ 2042 à partir du 22 octobre 2021

Découvrez Battlefield Portal, une toute nouvelle plateforme axée sur la communauté, où les joueurs peuvent changer les règles de la guerre en créant, partageant et découvrant des batailles inattendues issues du passé, du présent et du futur emblématiques de Battlefield.

Battlefield 2042 est un jeu de tir à la première personne qui marque le retour à la guerre totale emblématique de la franchise. Adaptez-vous et triomphez dans un futur proche où le chaos a changé le monde. Faites équipe et utilisez un arsenal de pointe sur des champs de bataille dynamiques d'une ampleur sans précédent, avec une destruction épique et jusqu'à 128 joueurs*.

Précommandez maintenant et obtenez un accès anticipé à la bêta ouverte et bien plus : http://x.ea.com/68944 

Plus d'infos sur Battlefield : http://x.ea.com/68674 

Regardez le trailer d'annonce officiel de Battlefield 2042 : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E 

Regardez le trailer de gameplay officiel de Battlefield 2042 : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss 

Suivez-nous sur Twitter : https://twitter.com/battlefieldEAFR 
Suivez-nous sur Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/battlefield 
Suivez-nous sur Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/battlefield 

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal
*Uniquement sur Xbox Series X|S, PC et PlayStation®5. 64 joueurs maximum sur Xbox One et PlayStation®4.
localizations.pl.title: Battlefield 2042 | Oficjalny zwiastun - Portal Battlefield
localizations.pl.description:
Graj w Battlefield™ 2042 od 22 października 2021 r.

Odkryj Portal Battlefield – zupełnie nową platformę społecznościową, na której gracze mogą zmieniać zasady wojny, tworząc, dzieląc się i odkrywając nieoczekiwane bitwy z kultowej przeszłości, teraźniejszości i przyszłości Battlefield.

Battlefield 2042 to pierwszoosobowa strzelanka będąca powrotem do All-Out-Warfare, z której słynie ta kultowa seria gier. Improwizuj i zwyciężaj w pogrążonym w chaosie świecie niedalekiej przyszłości. Skompletuj drużynę i przygotuj najnowocześniejszą broń do starć na dynamicznie zmieniających się, pełnych spektakularnych zniszczeń polach bitwy, na których naraz może walczyć 128 graczy*.

Zamów w przedsprzedaży już dziś, aby uzyskać wcześniejszy dostęp do otwartej bety i nie tylko: http://x.ea.com/68944 

Dowiedz się więcej o Battlefield: http://x.ea.com/68674 

Obejrzyj pierwszy zwiastun Battlefield 2042: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E 

Obejrzyj oficjalny zwiastun rozgrywki Battlefield 2042: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss 

Śledź nas na Twitterze: https://twitter.com/battlefield 
Śledź nas na Instagramie: https://www.instagram.com/battlefield 
Śledź nas na Facebooku: https://www.facebook.com/battlefield 

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal
*Tylko na Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation®5 oraz PC. W wersjach na Xbox One i PlayStation®4 maksymalna liczba graczy to 64.
localizations.ru.title: Battlefield 2042 | Battlefield Portal — официальный трейлер
localizations.ru.description:
Battlefield™ 2042 выходит 22 октября 2021 года.

Узнайте всё о Battlefield Portal — новой, управляемой сообществом платформе, где игроки смогут изменить правила ведения боя, создавая непредсказуемые сражения из легендарного прошлого, настоящего и будущего вселенной Battlefield и делиться ими друг с другом.

Battlefield 2042 — это шутер от первого лица, в котором серия возвращается к легендарным масштабным сражениям. Адаптируйтесь и преодолевайте трудности в будущем, где царит хаос. Отправляйтесь на невероятно масштабные и постоянно меняющиеся поля боя для 128 игроков* со своим отрядом и арсеналом новейших технологий.

Оформите предзаказ, чтобы получить ранний доступ к открытому бета-тестированию и не только: http://x.ea.com/68944 

Подробнее о Battlefield: http://x.ea.com/68674 

Смотреть официальный дебютный трейлер Battlefield 2042: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E 

Смотреть официальный трейлер игрового процесса Battlefield 2042: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss 

Подпишитесь на нас в Twitter: https://twitter.com/battlefield 
Подпишитесь на нас в Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/battlefield 
Подпишитесь на нас в Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/battlefield 

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal
* Поддерживается только на Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation®5 и ПК. На Xbox One и PlayStation®4 в одном сражении могут участвовать не более 64 игроков
localizations.ko.title: Battlefield 2042 | Battlefield Portal 공식 트레일러
localizations.ko.description:
2021년 10월 22일부터 Battlefield™ 2042를 플레이하세요

플레이어가 Battlefield의 대표적인 과거, 현재, 미래의 예상치 못한 전투를 만들고, 공유하고, 발견해 전쟁의 규칙을 바꿀 수 있는 새로운 커뮤니티 기반 플랫폼인 Battlefield Portal을 살펴보세요.

Battlefield 2042는 프랜차이즈의 상징인 전면전으로의 복귀를 알리는 1인칭 슈팅 게임입니다. 무질서로 변한 가까운 미래 세계에서 적응하고 극복하십시오. 128인 플레이어* 게임 지원, 시리즈 최대의 게임 규모, 엄청난 파괴 장면들을 지원하며 역동적으로 변화하는 전장에서 각자의 분대를 구성하고 최첨단 무기로 전투에 참여하세요.

지금 예약 구매하고 오픈 베타 사전 플레이 혜택 등을 받으세요: http://x.ea.com/68944 

Battlefield에 관해 더 알아보기: http://x.ea.com/68674 

Battlefield 2042 공식 공개 트레일러 감상하기: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E 

Battlefield 2042 공식 게임플레이 트레일러 감상하기: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss 

Twitter 팔로우: https://twitter.com/battlefield 
Instagram 팔로우: https://www.instagram.com/battlefield 
Facebook 팔로우: https://www.facebook.com/battlefield 

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #BattlefieldPortal
*Xbox Series X|S, PC, PlayStation®5에서 지원됩니다. Xbox One 및 PlayStation®4는 64인 플레이어만 지원합니다
localizations.es.title: Battlefield 2042 | Tráiler oficial de Portal de Battlefield
localizations.es.description:
Juega a Battlefield™ 2042 a partir del 22 de octubre de 2021

Descubre Portal de Battlefield: una nueva plataforma para la comunidad donde los jugadores pueden cambiar las reglas de la guerra creando, compartiendo y descubriendo batallas inesperadas del pasado, presente y futuro de Battlefield.

Battlefield 2042 es un shooter en primera persona que marca el regreso a la emblemática guerra total de la franquicia. Adáptate y sobrevive en un mundo en el futuro cercano transformado por el desorden. Forma tu patrulla y utiliza un arsenal de vanguardia en campos de batalla en constante cambio con 128 jugadores*, una escala sin precedentes y una destrucción épica.

Reserva ya para conseguir acceso anticipado a la Beta abierta y más: http://x.ea.com/68944

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #PortalBattlefield
*Compatible con Xbox Series X|S, PC y PlayStation®5. Xbox One y PlayStation®4 estarán limitadas a 64 jugadores.

snippet.title: Germany after the flooding | DW Documentary
snippet.description:
Germany is in shock. Days of heavy rain caused several rivers to burst their banks, flooding entire towns and villages. More than 160 people lost their lives. Now survivors are battling to clean up in the wake of the disaster. 

Several European countries have been hit by extreme weather, and many lives have been lost. Regions in western Germany have been most severely affected: in Rhineland-Palatinate, the south of North Rhine-Westphalia, and parts of Bavaria. The floodwaters destroyed highways, houses and whole communities. The floods have receded, leaving behind thick mud and tons of rubble. Chancellor Angela Merkel and other political leaders visited the disaster zones, offering encouragement and promising swift financial help for victims of the flooding. But many of those affected have criticized the emergency response as chaotic. In contrast, communities came together in solidarity – many people travelled long distances to offer their help. DW reporter Miodrag Soric visited the badly hit localities of Schuld and Walporzheim in Rhineland-Palatinate. He reports on how residents and volunteer helpers are dealing with the aftermath of the flooding. 

__

DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. Watch top documentaries from German broadcasters and international production companies. Meet intriguing people, travel to distant lands, get a look behind the complexities of daily life and build a deeper understanding of current affairs and global events. Subscribe and explore the world around you with DW Documentary.

snippet.title: Dead Space Official Teaser Trailer – EA Play Live 2021
snippet.description:
The sci-fi survival horror classic Dead Space returns, completely rebuilt from the ground up by Motive Studios to offer a deeper and more immersive experience. Harnessing the power of the Frostbite game engine and next generation consoles, this remake brings jaw-dropping visual fidelity and improvements to gameplay while staying true to the original. Dead Space will be available on PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC.

Isaac Clarke is an everyman engineer on a mission to repair a vast, sprawling starship, the USG Ishimura, only to discover something has gone horribly wrong. The ship's crew has been slaughtered and infected by some alien scourge...and Isaac’s beloved partner, Nicole, is lost somewhere on board.

Now Isaac is alone with only his tools and engineering skills as he attempts to uncover the nightmarish mystery of what happened aboard the Ishimura. Trapped with hostile creatures called “necromorphs”, Isaac faces a battle for survival, not only against the escalating terrors of the ship, but his own crumbling sanity. 

Official Website: https://www.ea.com/games/dead-space

Follow us on:
•Twitter – https://twitter.com/deadspace
•Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/deadspace
•Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/ea/

localizations.ja.title: 「Dead Space」公式ティーザートレーラー – EA Play Live 2021
localizations.ja.description:
SFサバイバルホラーの名作「Dead Space」が帰ってきます。Motive Studiosが1から再構築し、さらに奥深く没入感が増した体験をお届けします。Frostbiteゲームエンジンと次世代機の能力を活用。オリジナル作を損なうことのない形でビジュアルを忠実に再現し、ゲームプレイの改善を実施しています。「Dead Space」はPlayStation®5、Xbox Series X|S、PCでお楽しみいただけます。

ごく普通のエンジニア、アイザック・クラークは救難を求める巨大宇宙船、USG Ishimuraの復旧ミッションへと向かった。しかし、そこで目にしたものはあまりにも酷い惨状だった。

船員は切り裂かれ、エイリアンとおぼしき者に寄生されていた… そして、アイザックの恋人ニコルは行方不明に。
アイザックはたった独り、工具と技術力だけを頼りにIshimuraで起きた酷たらしい謎を解き明かそうとする。
「ネクロモーフ」と呼ばれる敵対クリーチャーに囲まれたアイザックは、生き残りをかけた戦いに身を投じる。船内に広がる恐怖に抗い、そして崩壊寸前の自我を保つ戦いに。

公式サイト: https://www.ea.com/ja-jp/games/dead-space

以下をフォロー:

•Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/deadspace
•Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/ea/
localizations.it.title: Teaser trailer ufficiale di Dead Space – EA Play Live 2021
localizations.it.description:
Ritorna il classico horror di sopravvivenza fantascientifico Dead Space, ricostruito da zero da Motive Studios per offrire un'esperienza di gioco più profonda e immersiva.
Sfruttando la potenza del motore di gioco Frostbite e delle console di nuova generazione, questo remake apporta miglioramenti alle dinamiche di gioco con una qualità grafica sbalorditiva pur restando fedele all'originale.
Dead Space sarà disponibile su PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S e PC.

Isaac Clarke è un semplice ingegnere in missione per riparare una grande nave spaziale, la USG Ishimura, per poi scoprire che qualcosa è andato terribilmente storto.
L'intero equipaggio è stato sterminato e infettato da una specie aliena... e l'amata compagna di Isaac, Nicole, è dispersa a bordo.

Ora Isaac è rimasto da solo con i suoi strumenti e con le sue competenze tecniche e dovrà cercare di svelare il mistero dietro l'incubo che si è scatenato a bordo dell'Ishimura. Intrappolato insieme a creature ostili chiamate "necromorfi", Isaac deve affrontare una battaglia per la sopravvivenza, non solo contro i crescenti orrori della nave, ma anche contro la sua sanità mentale sempre più fragile.

Sito web ufficiale: https://www.ea.com/it-it/games/dead-space/dead-space

Seguici su:
• Twitter – https://twitter.com/deadspace
• Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/deadspace
• Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/ea/
localizations.pt-BR.title: Teaser trailer oficial de Dead Space – EA Play Live de 2021
localizations.pt-BR.description:
O clássico de sobrevivência, terror e ficção científica Dead Space está de volta, totalmente reformulado pela Motive Studios para oferecer uma experiência mais aprofundada e imersiva. Aproveitando toda a potência do engine de jogo Frostbite e dos consoles da próxima geração, o remake confere fidelidade visual e melhorias impressionantes à jogabilidade, ao mesmo tempo que honra o original. Dead Space estará disponível para PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S e PC.

Isaac Clarke é um engenheiro comum que recebe a tarefa de consertar uma enorme nave espacial, a USG Ishimura. Chegando lá, descobre que alguma coisa está muito errada.

A tripulação foi massacrada e contaminada por algum tipo de praga alienígena...e a namorada de Isaac, Nicole, está perdida em algum lugar da nave.
Isaac está sozinho e só conta com suas ferramentas e habilidades de engenharia para desvendar o mistério horripilante do que aconteceu a bordo da Ishimura.

Preso com criaturas hostis conhecidas como "necromorfos", Isaac enfrenta uma batalha pela sobrevivência, não só contra a maré de horrores na nave, mas também a própria sanidade, prestes a se esgotar.

Site oficial: https://www.ea.com/pt-br/games/dead-space

•Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/deadspace
•Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ea/
localizations.pl.title: Oficjalny zwiastun Dead Space – EA Play Live 2021
localizations.pl.description:
Klasyczny horror science fiction Dead Space powraca w zupełnie nowej odsłonie - Motive Studios przygotowało jeszcze bardziej immersyjną rozgrywkę.Dzięki mocy silnika Frostbite i konsol następnej generacji, nowa wersja gry zapewni niezrównaną grafikę i ulepszenia rozgrywki, jednocześnie zachowując wierność oryginałowi.
Dead Space pojawi się na PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S i PC.

Isaac Clark jest zwykłym inżynierem, któremu powierzono misję naprawy ogromnego statku kosmicznego: USG Ishimura. Sprawy przybrały jednak tragiczny obrót.
Załoga została wymordowana i zainfekowana kosmiczną plagą… a Nicole, ukochana partnerka Isaaca, zaginęła gdzieś na pokładzie.

Osamotniony Isaac jedynie przy pomocy swoich narzędzi i umiejętności inżynieryjnych usiłuje rozwikłać koszmarną tajemnicę wydarzeń na pokładzie Ishimury.
Uwięziony z wrogimi „nekromorfami”, musi podjąć walkę o przetrwanie – nie tylko w obliczu coraz straszniejszych niebezpieczeństw na statku, ale też z powoli nadciągającym szaleństwem.

localizations.ru.title: Официальный тизер Dead Space – EA Play Live 2021
localizations.ru.description:
Культовая научно-фантастическая игра в жанре ужасов возвращается. Motive Studios воссоздала Dead Space с нуля, сделав игровой процесс ещё более глубоким и захватывающим. Благодаря игровому движку Frostbite и мощности консолей нового поколения разработчики смогли продемонстрировать неповторимый уровень визуализации и усовершенствовать игровой процесс, сохранив при этом дух оригинала. Dead Space выйдет на PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S и ПК.

Айзек Кларк — рядовой инженер, отправленный на огромный космический корабль USG «Ишимура» для проведения ремонтных работ, по прибытии на который он узнаёт об ужасной трагедии.
Весь экипаж оказался перебит и заражён инопланетной скверной, а возлюбленная Айзека, Николь, пропала где-то на борту.
В распоряжении Айзека только его инструменты и инженерные навыки, и с помощью них ему предстоит раскрыть ужасную тайну произошедшего на борту «Ишимуры».

Запертый в замкнутом пространстве с враждебными «некроморфами» Айзек вынужден вступить в борьбу за собственное выживание и противостоять не только заполонившим корабль жутким тварям, но и медленно подступающему безумию.

Официальный сайт: https://www.ea.com/ru-ru/games/dead-space

Подписывайтесь на нас:
• Twitter — https://twitter.com/deadspace
• Facebook — https://www.facebook.com/deadspace
• Instagram — https://www.instagram.com/ea/
localizations.es-MX.title: Teaser trailer oficial de Dead Space - EA Play Live 2021
localizations.es-MX.description:
Regresa el clásico de horror de supervivencia Dead Space, completamente renovado desde cero por Motive Studios a fin de ofrecer una experiencia más profunda y envolvente.
Aprovechando la tecnología del motor de juegos Frostbite y las consolas de última generación, esta remake trae consigo gráficos deslumbrantes y mejoras de jugabilidad, siempre manteniendo la fidelidad al original. Dead Space estará disponible en PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S y PC.

Isaac Clarke es un ingeniero cualquiera con la misión de reparar una vasta nave, la USG Ishimura, en la que descubrirá que algo salió terriblemente mal.
La tripulación ha sido descuartizada e infectada por una amenaza alienígena… y la pareja amada de Isaac, Nicole, se perdió en alguna parte de la nave.

Ahora, Isaac solo cuenta con sus herramientas y habilidades de ingeniería para revelar el terrorífico misterio de lo que sucedió abordo de la Ishimura. Atrapado con criaturas hostiles denominadas "necromorfos", Isaac enfrentará una batalla por la supervivencia, no solo contra los crecientes peligros de la nave, sino también con su propia cordura. Sitio web oficial: https://www.ea.com/es-mx/games/dead-space

Síguenos en:

•Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/ea/
localizations.fr-FR.title: Dead Space – Bande-annonce officielle – EA Play Live 2021
localizations.fr-FR.description:
Dead Space, grand classique du genre « survival horror » dans l'espace, est de retour dans une version entièrement reconstruite par Motive Studios pour une expérience plus riche et plus immersive que jamais. Grâce à la puissance du moteur Frostbite et des consoles de la nouvelle génération, ce remake offre des graphismes d'un réalisme époustouflant et apporte de nombreuses améliorations à la jouabilité tout en restant fidèle à l'esprit du jeu original.
Dead Space sera disponible sur PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S et PC.

Simple ingénieur chargé de réparer l'USG Ishimura, un gigantesque vaisseau spatial, Isaac Clarke va vite comprendre que les choses ont très, très mal tourné.
L'équipage a été massacré et infecté par un fléau extraterrestre... et Nicole, sa partenaire bien-aimée, est perdue quelque part à bord du vaisseau.

Uniquement armé de ses outils et de ses compétences scientifiques, Isaac va tenter de découvrir la cauchemardesque vérité qui se cache à bord de l'Ishimura.
Pour y parvenir, il devra non seulement lutter pour sa survie face aux créatures hostiles appelées « nécromorphes », mais aussi préserver sa santé mentale en dépit des horreurs indicibles qui se dresseront sur sa route.

Site Internet officiel : https://www.ea.com/games/dead-space

Suivez-nous:
•Twitter – https://twitter.com/deadspace
•Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/deadspace
•Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/ea/
localizations.de-DE.title: Offizieller Teaser-Trailer zu Dead Space – EA Play Live 2021
localizations.de-DE.description:
Der SF-Survival-Horrorklassiker Dead Space ist wieder da – von Motive Studios neu umgesetzt für ein noch immersiveres Spielerlebnis. Mit der Leistung der Frostbite-Engine und der Konsolen der nächsten Generation bietet dieses Remake atemberaubende grafische Qualität und verbessertes Gameplay, wobei es dem Original treu bleibt.
Dead Space wird auf PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S und PC verfügbar sein.

Isaac Clarke ist ein Techniker mit der Mission, ein riesiges Raumschiff – die USG Ishimura – zu reparieren. Doch etwas ist schiefgelaufen. Die Besatzung des Schiffes wurde massakriert und mit einer außerirdischen Plage infiziert – und Isaacs geliebte Partnerin Nicole befindet sich irgendwo an Bord.

Jetzt muss Isaac nur mit seinen Werkzeugen und seiner Ingenieurskunst das grausige Rätsel um die Geschehnisse auf der Ishimura lösen. Umgeben von feindseligen Kreaturen namens „Nekromorphs“ muss er ums Überleben kämpfen, gegen die Schrecken auf dem Schiff und den drohenden Wahnsinn.

Offizielle Website: https://www.ea.com/de-de/games/dead-space

Folge uns auf:
•Twitter – https://twitter.com/deadspace
•Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/deadspace
•Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/ea/
localizations.es-ES.title: Tráiler oficial del teaser de Dead Space – EA Play Live 2021
localizations.es-ES.description:
Regresa el clásico videojuego de terror y supervivencia Dead Space, completamente renovado por Motive Studios para ofrecer una mayor experiencia inmersiva. Aprovechando la potencia del motor de juego de Frostbite y las consolas de nueva generación, la nueva versión cuenta con una fidelidad gráfica impresionante y mejoras en el juego mientras mantiene la esencia original.
Dead Space estará disponible en PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S y PC.

Isaac Clarke es el típico ingeniero que tiene la misión de reparar una nave de inmensas proporciones, la USG Ishimura, cuando descubre que algo horrible ha pasado.
La tripulación de la nave ha sido masacrada e infectada por algún tipo de plaga alienígena... Además, Nicole, la pareja sentimental de Isaac, está perdida en algún lugar de la nave.

Ahora Isaac, solo con sus herramientas y habilidades de ingeniería, tendrá que intentar resolver el espeluznante misterio de lo que ha ocurrido a bordo de Ishimura.
Atrapado con criaturas enemigas llamadas "necromorfos", Isaac debe luchar por sobrevivir a los terrores de la nave cada vez mayores y a su cordura cada vez más frágil.
Sitio web oficial: https://www.ea.com/es-es/games/dead-space

Síguenos en:
•Twitter – https://twitter.com/deadspace
•Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/deadspace
•Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/ea/
localizations.nl-NL.title: Officiële teaser-trailer Dead Space – EA Play Live 2021
localizations.nl-NL.description:
De sci-fi survival horrorklassieker Dead Space keert terug, helemaal opnieuw ontwikkeld door Motive Studios, voor een diepere en meeslependere ervaring. Deze remake blijft trouw aan het origineel maar biedt een verbluffend visueel realisme en verbeteringen in de gameplay, dankzij de kracht van de Frostbite-engine en next-gen consoles.
Dead Space is verkrijgbaar voor PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S en PC.

Isaac Clarke is een alledaagse ingenieur die een reusachtig sterrenschip, de USG Ishimura, moet repareren, maar hij ontdekt dat er iets gruwelijk mis is gegaan.
De bemanning van het schip is afgeslacht en geïnfecteerd door een buitenaardse plaag... en Isaac's geliefde partner, Nicole, is ergens aan boord verdwenen. Nu heeft Isaac alleen zijn gereedschap en technische vaardigheden, en moet hij proberen te ontrafelen welke nachtmerrie er heeft plaatsgevonden aan boord van de Ishimura.

Gevangen tussen vijandige wezens, ‘necromorphs’ genaamd, moet Isaac strijden om te overleven, niet alleen tegen de escalerende verschrikkingen van het schip, maar ook tegen zijn eigen afbrokkelende geestelijke gezondheid.

Officiële website: https://www.ea.com/nl-nl/games/dead-space

Volg ons op:
•Twitter – https://twitter.com/deadspace
•Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/deadspace
•Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/ea/
localizations.sv.title: Dead Space officiell förhandstrailer – EA Play Live 2021
localizations.sv.description:
Dead Space, den klassiska överlevnadsskräckisen i scifi-miljö, är tillbaka. Helt återuppbyggd från grunden av Motive Studios för att ge en ännu djupare och mer engagerande upplevelse. Med kraften från spelmotorn Frostbite och nästa generations spelkonsoler ger denna remake en visuell skärpa och spelförbättringar som får dig att tappa hakan, samtidigt som den är trogen originalet.
Dead Space kommer att släppas till PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S och PC.

Isaac Clarke är en helt vanlig tekniker med uppdrag att reparera det enorma rymdskeppet USG Ishimura, men han upptäcker att något har gått fruktansvärt fel.
Besättningen på skeppet har slaktats och infekterats av en utomjordisk farsot ... och Isaacs älskade partner Nicole har gått vilse ombord.

Nu står Isaac ensam med sina verktyg och sitt tekniska kunnande, medan han försöker avslöja det mardrömslika mysteriet med vad som hände ombord på Ishimura.
Instängd med de fientliga varelser som kallas "necromorfer" kämpar Isaac för sin överlevnad, både i strid mot skeppets eskalerande fasor och för att försöka undvika att bli helt galen. 

Officiell webbplats: https://www.ea.com/sv-se/games/dead-space

•Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/deadspace
•Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/ea/

snippet.title: I Played Minecraft With Hank From Breaking Bad
snippet.description:
GET MY HOODIE AT: https://www.quackity.shop/

JESSE! Hank from Breaking Bad is playing Minecraft, this is bad for the operation. Just kidding, it's great because Minecraft is the game Hank from Breaking Bad is playing today along with GeorgeNotFound who is also in the Dream Minecraft Dream Manhunt videos and GeorgeNotFound never wins by the way which is funny, and BadBoyHalo another friend who is also in the Dream Minecraft Manhunt Videos. Hank Breaking Bad AKA Dean Norris is one of the funniest Minecraft players I know, I actually love Hank Breaking Bad and Breaking Bad the show, it is very good. So now that we have Hank Breaking Bad playing Minecraft with me Quackity, GeorgeNotFound, and BadBoyHalo, this is simply the best day of my life.

All jokes aside, Breaking Bad is one of my favorite shows of all time, without a doubt. To be able to have the honor of having Dean Norris play Minecraft with me still doesn't feel real. I'll tell you firsthand he is one of the sweetest kindest guys ever, and even though I put him through this pain of being in this silly video, he was so kind about everything. Dean Norris 4 evr.

After trailing by 5 at halftime, the Bucks outscored the Suns by 12 in the second half. Giannis Antetokounmpo took home the MVP after dropping 50 points, 14 rebounds and 5 blocks. snippet.localized.description:
The Milwaukee Bucks completed their comeback against the Phoenix Suns last night, winning their fourth in a row to win their second championship and first since 1971. After trailing by 5 at halftime, the Bucks outscored the Suns by 12 in the second half. Giannis Antetokounmpo took home the MVP after dropping 50 points, 14 rebounds and 5 blocks. snippet.title: Ariana Grande - positions (Official Live Performance) | Vevo
snippet.description:
Ariana Grande - positions (Official Live Performance) | Vevo

If our Official Live Performances of “pov” and “safety net” reveal anything, it’s that Ariana Grande excels at her job because she’s so passionate about the results. You don’t hit the high notes, you don’t exude candor, and you don’t make pop music as moving as she does without crossing the T’s and dotting the I’s. A very cool Cali session with the look and feel of a cozy little meadow was a perfect place to turn some of the best tunes on ‘Positions’ into utterly memorable performances. Go Team Ari. In a typically inventive move, our hero chose to loop her vocals when it came time to perform the album’s title track. Watch her augment the band’s moves with a little layering of her voice. As she references both the kitchen and the bedroom in her lyrics, the sound stacks up, taking on its own internal rhythm. Beautiful.

The Vevo official live performance of “positions" by Ariana Grande. Listen & download positions (the album) here: http://arianagrande.lnk.to/positions

snippet.title: Traveling to a Country that was Closed for 40 Years
snippet.description:
For your chance to win a Zelectric Porsche 912 E and support a great cause, enter at https://omaze.com/YesTheory 

Thomas spent 7 days exploring around the countryside of Albania in the search for some of the abandoned bunkers left behind after the the communist dictator Enver Hoxha's brutal rule from the 1940's to the 1980's. Yet what we found after a few days was so much more than we'd originally come for. The nature, the kindness of the people and the rich history blew us away. We still left wondering what the future of these bunkers holds...

Check out Nathaniel's channel here!!
https://www.youtube.com/c/nathanieldrewofficial/videos

Thank you to Cory Martin for once again making the visuals in this story look INCREDIBLE:
https://www.instagram.com/cory.s.martin

https://www.instagram.com/lenanikolaj_

Thank you to Drive Albania for showing us around the country!
https://www.instagram.com/drivealbania
https://www.instagram.com/ardi_zhugjeli

snippet.title: Lorde - Stoned at the Nail Salon (Visualiser)
snippet.description:
Stoned at the Nail Salon out now https://lorde.lnk.to/StonedAtTheNailSalon 
New album Solar Power out August 20th, 2021, pre-order now: https://lorde.lnk.to/SPAlbum

The Solar Power Tour is on sale now - get dates and tickets: https://www.lorde.co.nz/tour

Sign up to the Solar Power Institute Bulletin: https://www.lorde.co.nz/sign-up 

Website: https://www.lorde.co.nz/ 
Tour Dates: https://www.lorde.co.nz/tour 
Bulletin: https://www.lorde.co.nz/sign-up 
 
 
STONED AT THE NAIL SALON (LYRICS )
 
Got a wishbone drying on the windowsill in my kitchen  
Just in case I wake up and realise I’ve chosen wrong  
I love this life that I have  
The vine hanging over the door  
And the dog who comes when I call  
But I wonder sometimes what I’m missing 
 
My hot blood’s been burning for so many summers now 
It’s time to cool it down   
Wherever that leads  
 
‘Cause all the beautiful girls, they will fade like the roses  
And all the times they will change, it’ll all come around 
I don’t know 
Maybe I’m just stoned at the nail salon 
Maybe I’m just stoned at the nail salon again 
 
Got a memory of waiting in your bed wearing only my earrings  
We’d go dancing all over the land mines under our town  
But the sun has to rise  
When it does, we’ll divide up the papers  
Two former hell-raisers  
I’m still crazy for you, babe 
 
My hot blood’s been burning for so many summers now 
It’s time to cool it down   
Wherever that leads  
 
‘Cause all the music you loved at sixteen, you’ll grow out of  
And all the times they will change, it’ll all come around 
I don’t know 
Maybe I’m just stoned at the nail salon 
Maybe I’m just stoned at the nail salon again 
 
Oh, make it good  
Oh, make it good 
I’d ride and I’d ride on the carousel round and round forever if I could  
But it’s time to cool it down  
Whatever that means 
 
Spend all the evenings you can with the people who raised you 
Cause all the times they will change, it’ll all come around 
I don’t know 
Maybe I’m just stoned at the nail salon 
Maybe I’m just stoned at the nail salon again

#Lorde #SolarPower #StonedAtTheNailSalon
